          	  <a href="artical-src12151.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(1)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12151.htm">發刊辭 [ HOAT-KHAN-SÛ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">發刊辭
 
對主後1872年偕牧師到北部台灣設教到今，已經有53</span&g...<a href="artical-12151.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
